cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SD, cs.CE 

The paper uses Artificial Neural Networks (ANN) to predict solar irradiation, which is a popular technique in the field of Artificial Intelligence (AI). Therefore, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely categories. The paper also deals with forecasting, which falls under the category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves simulations, which can be categorized under cs.SD (Software Development). Finally, the paper deals with the performance of PV power grids, which can be categorized under cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
